title: Colin Cowherd Podcast - Colin’s Week 5 NFL Instant Reaction
itunes:title: Colin Cowherd Podcast - Colin’s Week 5 NFL Instant Reaction
description:
Colin gives his instant reaction to the biggest game from the slate of Week 5 NFL games, including why the haters won’t give Lamar Jackson credit for winning ugly, where the often maligned Cowboys HC Mike McCarthy has been better than expected, more bad signs from the Packers in their disappointing London loss to the Giants, the most impressive thing about Brian Daboll’s early season NY turnaround, and if the Niners and Jimmy G are the best team in the NFC.

Follow Colin and The Volume on Twitter for the latest content and updates and check out FanDuel for the best wagering and daily fantasy action! #Herd #Volume
